title: Region / state roundup : Former Princess Anne High star changes his mind , will transfer to UNLV instead of Michigan State
body_text:
Getting your Trinity Audio player ready...
Defensive back Tony Grimes played three seasons at North Carolina and then transferred to Texas A&M, but he didn't play last season due to an injury.
